txt.en: 'It cannot be, [placeholder]. Thaurlach cannot be back. He was defeated...'
'Do you hear that? Sounds like the shuffling of feet from the hallway.'
'[placeholder], let us continue to push forward. There has to be some sort of clue to Glorfindel's whereabouts.'
'That chest in the middle of the room has been rummaged through, perhaps that is the clue we've been seeking!'
'Glorfindel must have found what he came here for. Perhaps we will find him through that door straight ahead, [placeholder]!'
'We have found Glorfindel, but -- what is that?'
'We are not finding any clues, only more danger. Take out those Darklings!'
